{"tid":657462,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"挖礦公司Coulla 派幣手法公開? (1)  覺得係唔係騙局?","createTime":"2018-05-08T06:32:47.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-05T10:38:11.000Z","uid":90156,"like":88,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":42,"replies":[{"pid":"f230453b88ba6283c1bfa53dc75eb97ebd9aab64","tid":657462,"uid":90156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T06:32:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/653466/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/653466/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n呢個係我第一個Post , Coulla 己發出聲名 話係有機 同埋要告我<br />\n<br />\n雖然創辦人上黎貼左假圖比人踢爆 懷疑犯左不誠實使用電腦<br />\n詳情<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/655607/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/655607/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n不過今日唔講呢樣野 <br />\n<br />\n介紹番<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">挖礦公司Coulla 派幣手法公開?</span><br />\n<br />\n我地係挖礦公司Coulla Facebook搵到2位人兄貼出黎既圖<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/08/124629_f7b4c51bfa7d13ab8682f630af9c4ad1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F08%2F124629_f7b4c51bfa7d13ab8682f630af9c4ad1.jpg&h=7e34ccd1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/08/124629_e79741907ab386074ee109675f737b09.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F08%2F124629_e79741907ab386074ee109675f737b09.JPG&h=435eff71&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n分別有創辦人Ronald Ng 同官方AC留言認證左<br />\n<br />\n我地細心去睇下兩張圖<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/08/124817_b1810bb4cee4b5ccbc2192d4106f68ac.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F08%2F124817_b1810bb4cee4b5ccbc2192d4106f68ac.jpg&h=d867ef21&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">點解同一份合約 GARY 收到既幣會多過阿MAN? </span></span><br />\n<br />\n咁正路應該收到幾多幣先啱?<br />\n<br />\n我地睇番ETH當日既難度先<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/08/125109_3304fbe033b34f70e7905f0f4300e82f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F08%2F125109_3304fbe033b34f70e7905f0f4300e82f.jpg&h=73ae0d63&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n再去計下合約150MHS當日既收益先<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n1月16號 150MHS 應收0.0177   兩人分別收到0.015 及 0.014<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/08/125234_f01eb8af0dd4c75dd91534def15aa027.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F08%2F125234_f01eb8af0dd4c75dd91534def15aa027.JPG&h=c13cce2e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1月19號  150MHS 應收0.0171   兩人分別收到0.0146及0.0136<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/08/125240_53d41fb042e9011a9624d53a560ec590.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F08%2F125240_53d41fb042e9011a9624d53a560ec590.JPG&h=2a7e4ceb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1月22號   150MHS 應收0.0162   兩人分別收到0.0138及0.0129<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/08/125243_9358f18bad51550f47ed130366d30a84.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F08%2F125243_9358f18bad51550f47ed130366d30a84.JPG&h=38791816&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">GARY就收少左20%到左右  MAN就慘啲收少左30%左右</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">阿MAN 你係唔係得罪左Ronald阿?</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/08/135623_f5a6908bc4744c13ad66bd94cb89d595.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F08%2F135623_f5a6908bc4744c13ad66bd94cb89d595.JPG&h=0d3f964c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n獨有既混合挖掘 無派多之餘 仲要少左2~3成? <br />\n良心公司<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/08/140528_da79bd88c357b74432e6161eb648b9ed.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F08%2F140528_da79bd88c357b74432e6161eb648b9ed.JPG&h=fe3f0e82&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n拿拿拿 你自己叫人上外國Calculator網到CHECK架 唔好話我屈你阿<br />\n<br />\n眼淚 在心裹流<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/08/140702_3615a32a0d3e8d0891322748d0e5a904.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F08%2F140702_3615a32a0d3e8d0891322748d0e5a904.JPG&h=62202d85&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/QYLtR45.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FQYLtR45.gif&h=b66e97a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">有冇諗過同一份合約兩個月內 會有3.6萬 4.2萬 4.8萬既唔同價錢 之外 仲有唔同派幣既數量?</span></strong>"},{"pid":"2d440350d75a58995752c2b7aa9f6d9f2cd2935d","tid":657462,"uid":145923,"like":22,"dislike":1,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T06:38:22.000Z","msg":"這類合約,好有機會構成非法集資,建議向証監會舉報."},{"pid":"e646f97515dc55d40beb1c5516d3dbf6979d1354","tid":657462,"uid":90156,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T06:42:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.coinwarz.com/calculators/ethereum-mining-calculator\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.coinwarz.com%2Fcalculators%2Fethereum-mining-calculator&d=UO09%2BoZJNK498c%2Bwp3OlmDA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=301c263b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.coinwarz.com/calculators/ethereum-mining-calculator</a><br />\n<br />\n唔信既可以計下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a73b10f5c0ec9671af7b6e22653915c522527e88","tid":657462,"uid":37135,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T06:46:48.000Z","msg":"ching 好波"},{"pid":"4a66f76e57466f448390ceb8754552e41f516855","tid":657462,"uid":55598,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T06:52:42.000Z","msg":"推到佢仆街"},{"pid":"e795f2ec844693ad17a02c2523a24ae5f7401a2e","tid":657462,"uid":87073,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T06:58:07.000Z","msg":"阿man<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebe8127ff410ab08efdda916748944cdfcaaf031","tid":657462,"uid":185360,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T07:04:47.000Z","msg":"佢個套利模式無懈可擊<br />\n幾乎冇輸既可能性"},{"pid":"f7311e64e12f093ff57c253fb35baf0b5ca9dce3","tid":657462,"uid":129169,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T07:12:53.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68a8b5def6f587b168722e8bc12619c06b29e013","tid":657462,"uid":129169,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"ebe8127ff410ab08efdda916748944cdfcaaf031","tid":657462,"uid":185360,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T07:04:47.000Z","msg":"佢個套利模式無懈可擊<br />\n幾乎冇輸既可能性"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T07:14:08.000Z","msg":"根本就係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n錢已袋，拿拿林買一堆返黎，再慢慢派，根本係集資投資，無本生利<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcc5843a45044a453938b7d568e9c1bd0563deaf","tid":657462,"uid":185360,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"68a8b5def6f587b168722e8bc12619c06b29e013","tid":657462,"uid":129169,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"ebe8127ff410ab08efdda916748944cdfcaaf031","tid":657462,"uid