https://eservices.customs.gov.hk/MSOS/download/guideline/Licensing_Guide_zh_TW.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Feservices.customs.gov.hk%2FMSOS%2Fdownload%2Fguideline%2FLicensing_Guide_zh_TW.pdf&d=UO09%2BoZJNK498c%2Bwp3OlmDA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=9c208b3f\" target=\"_blank\">https://eservices.customs.gov.hk/MSOS/download/guideline/Licensing_Guide_zh_TW.pdf</a><br />\n拿海關個金錢服務經營者牌照指引就係度<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://big5.xinhuanet.com/gate/big5/www.cs.com.cn/gg/201802/t20180205_5700633.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbig5.xinhuanet.com%2Fgate%2Fbig5%2Fwww.cs.com.cn%2Fgg%2F201802%2Ft20180205_5700633.html&d=UO09%2BoZJNK498c%2Bwp3OlmDA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=49d22af3\" target=\"_blank\">http://big5.xinhuanet.com/gate/big5/www.cs.com.cn/gg/201802/t20180205_5700633.html</a><br />\n香港證監會：監管虛擬貨幣交易有清晰指引<br />\n作者：來源：證券時報APP2018-02-05 19:04<br />\n　　香港證監會行政總裁歐達禮5日表示，在剛剛過去的兩、三個月裏，市場各方對虛擬貨幣的看法出現很大轉變，國際社會正考慮對其加強監管以保障投資者利益。歐達禮強調，香港證監會對此有清晰的指引，如果涉及證券或集體投資計劃（CIS）等，香港證監會將會以現行監管手段作出處理。<br />\n<br />\n[url]<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%B6%93%E6%BF%9F/158419/%E8%AD%89%E7%9B%A3%E6%9C%83-%E5%B7%B2%E9%87%9D%E5%B0%8D%E8%99%9B%E6%93%AC%E8%B2%A8%E5%B9%A3%E4%BA%A4%E6%98%93%E6%89%80%E5%8F%8Aico%E6%8E%A1%E7%9B%A3%E7%AE%A1%E8%A1%8C%E5%8B%95\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25B6%2593%25E6%25BF%259F%2F158419%2F%25E8%25AD%2589%25E7%259B%25A3%25E6%259C%2583-%25E5%25B7%25B2%25E9%2587%259D%25E5%25B0%258D%25E8%2599%259B%25E6%2593%25AC%25E8%25B2%25A8%25E5%25B9%25A3%25E4%25BA%25A4%25E6%2598%2593%25E6%2589%2580%25E5%258F%258Aico%25E6%258E%25A1%25E7%259B%25A3%25E7%25AE%25A1%25E8%25A1%258C%25E5%258B%2595&d=UO09%2BoZJNK498c%2Bwp3OlmDA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=531643a1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%B6%93%E6%BF%9F/158419/%E8%AD%89%E7%9B%A3%E6%9C%83-%E5%B7%B2%E9%87%9D%E5%B0%8D%E8%99%9B%E6%93%AC%E8%B2%A8%E5%B9%A3%E4%BA%A4%E6%98%93%E6%89%80%E5%8F%8Aico%E6%8E%A1%E7%9B%A3%E7%AE%A1%E8%A1%8C%E5%8B%95</a><br />\n[/url]證監會：已針對虛擬貨幣交易所及ICO採監管行動<br />\n撰文：文顥宗<br />\n2018-02-09 12:45<br />\n最後更新日期：2018-02-09 12:26<br />\n證監會公布，已就多間加密貨幣交易所及部分首次代幣發行（Initial Coin Offerings，ICO）發行人採取了監管行動。<br />\n已獲7間加密貨幣交易所確認或糾正<br />\n證監會稱，去年9月至今，已致函7間位於香港或與香港有連繫的加密貨幣交易所，警告它們不應在未領有牌照的情況下買賣屬於「證券」的加密貨幣，並獲大部分交易所確認或糾正。證監會亦先後致函7個ICO發行人，它們大多已確認遵從監管制度，或已即時停止向香港投資者發售代幣。<br />\n證監會強調會在適當的情況下，尤其對漠視《證券及期貨條例》相關條文的加密貨幣交易所和重犯者，可能會採取進一步行動。證監會透露曾接獲投資者投訴，內容涉及無法提取資金、資產遭挪用、交易所技術故障等。證監會呼籲，投資者應全面了解加密貨幣及ICO的風險，並注意有關價格大幅波動、遭黑客入侵及欺詐的風險正日漸增加。<br />\n<br />\n見到間良心公司仲搞埋加密貨幣找換店 進行買賣<br />\n<a href=\"https://shop.coulla.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fshop.coulla.com%2F&d=UO09%2BoZJNK498c%2Bwp3OlmDA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=d9ec76ad\" target=\"_blank\">https://shop.coulla.com/</a><br />\n<br />\n唔知佢有咩牌照呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係咪可以報哂海關同SFC呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"128dcdae8d276ea14bb8e645bbd54db4ac4157a8","tid":657462,"uid":84840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T15:48:43.000Z","msg":"佢個網乜鳩都冇<br />\n牌照號碼又冇 海關個持牌金錢服務經營者又搵唔到佢名<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"384be121c1f059a0bbed29da63d34d075e071bbb","tid":657462,"uid":90156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4c509f78fdbbd9311390335aef1098916d1cfa9d","tid":657462,"uid":84840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T15:45:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://eservices.customs.gov.hk/MSOS/download/guideline/Licensing_Guide_zh_TW.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Feservices.customs.gov.hk%2FMSOS%2Fdownload%2Fguideline%2FLicensing_Guide_zh_TW.pdf&d=UO09%2BoZJNK498c%2Bwp3OlmDA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=9c208b3f\" target=\"_blank\">https://eservices.customs.gov.hk/MSOS/download/guideline/Licensing_Guide_zh_TW.pdf</a><br />\n拿海關個金錢服務經營者牌照指引就係度<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://big5.xinhuanet.com/gate/big5/www.cs.com.cn/gg/201802/t20180205_5700633.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbig5.xinhuanet.com%2Fgate%2Fbig5%2Fwww.cs.com.cn%2Fgg%2F201802%2Ft20180205_5700633.html&d=UO09%2BoZJNK498c%2Bwp3OlmDA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=49d22af3\" target=\"_blank\">http://big5.xinhuanet.com/gate/big5/www.cs.com.cn/gg/201802/t20180205_5700633.html</a><br />\n香港證監會：監管虛擬貨幣交易有清晰指引<br />\n作者：來源：證券時報APP2018-02-05 19:04<br />\n　　香港證監會行政總裁歐達禮5日表示，在剛剛過去的兩、三個月裏，市場各方對虛擬貨幣的看法出現很大轉變，國際社會正考慮對其加強監管以保障投資者利益。歐達禮強調，香港證監會對此有清晰的指引，如果涉及證券或集體投資計劃（CIS）等，香港證監會將會以現行監管手段作出處理。<br />\n<br />\n[url]<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%B6%93%E6%BF%9F/158419/%E8%AD%89%E7%9B%A3%E6%9C%83-%E5%B7%B2%E9%87%9D%E5%B0%8D%E8%99%9B%E6%93%AC%E8%B2%A8%E5%B9%A3%E4%BA%A4%E6%98%93%E6%89%80%E5%8F%8Aico%E6%8E%A1%E7%9B%A3%E7%AE%A1%E8%A1%8C%E5%8B%95\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25B6%2593%25E6%25BF%259F%2F158419%2F%25E8%25AD%2589%25E7%259B%25A3%25E6%259C%2583-%25E5%25B7%25B2%25E9%2587%259D%25E5%25B0%258D%25E8%2599%259B%25E6%2593%25AC%25E8%25B2%25A8%25E5%25B9%25A3%25E4%25BA%25A4%25E6%2598%2593%25E6%2589%2580%25E5%258F%258Aico%25E6%258E%25A1%25E7%259B%25A3%25E7%25AE%25A1%25E8%25A1%258C%25E5%258B%2595&d=UO09%2BoZJNK498c%2Bwp3OlmDA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=531643a1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%B6%93%E6%BF%9F/158419/%E8%AD%89%E7%9B%A3%E6%9C%83-%E5%B7%B2%E9%87%9D%E5%B0%8D%E8%99%9B%E6%93%AC%E8%B2%A8%E5%B9%A3%E4%BA%A4%E6%98%93%E6%89%80%E5%8F%8Aico%E6%8E%A1%E7%9B%A3%E7%AE%A1%E8%A1%8C%E5%8B%95</a><br />\n[/url]證監會：已針對虛擬貨幣交易所及ICO採監管行動<br />\n撰文：文顥宗<br />\n2018-02-09 12:45<br />\n最後更新日期：2018-02-09 12:26<br />\n證監會公布，已就多間加密貨幣交易所及部分首次代幣發行（Initial Coin Offerings，ICO）發行人採取了監管行動。<br />\n已獲7間加密貨幣交易所確認或糾正<br />\n證監會稱，去年9月至今，已致函7間位於香港或與香港有連繫的加密貨幣交易所，警告它們不應在未領有牌照的情況下買賣屬於「證券」的加密貨幣，並獲大部分交易所確認或糾正。證監會亦先後致函7個ICO發行人，它們大多已確認遵從監管制度，或已即時停止向香港投資者發售代幣。<br />\n證監會強調會在適當的情況下，尤其對漠視《證券及期貨條例》相關條文的加密貨幣交易所和重犯者，可能會採取進一步行動。證監會透露曾接獲投資者投訴，內容涉及無法提取資金、資產遭挪用、交易所技術故障等。證監會呼籲，投資者應全面了解加密貨幣及ICO的風險，並注意有關價格大幅波動、遭黑客入侵及欺詐的風險正日漸增加。<br />\n<br />\n見到間良心公司仲搞埋加密貨幣找換店 進行買賣<br />\n<a href=\"https://shop.coulla.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fshop.coulla.com%2F&d=UO09%2BoZJNK498c%2Bwp3OlmDA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=d9ec76ad\" target=\"_blank\">https://shop.coulla.com/</a><br />\n<br />\n唔知佢有咩牌照呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係咪可以報哂海關同SFC呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T15:52:42.000Z","msg":"send email去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17db7df66182d8edfa49108f416f2a6f672f7bbc","tid":657462,"uid":84840,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T15:55:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.sfc.hk/web/TC/lodge-a-complaint/against-intermediaries-and-market-activities/complaint-form/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sfc.hk%2Fweb%2FTC%2Flodge-a-complaint%2Fagainst-intermediaries-and-market-activities%2Fcomplaint-form%2F&d=UO09%2BoZJNK498c%2Bwp3OlmDA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=47fb8f28\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.sfc.hk/web/TC/lodge-a-complaint/against-intermediaries-and-market-activities/complaint-form/</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">其實上網填投訴表格好快<br />\n大家一齊填填佢</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"36fe3c6468a27160b8cc2ec7aa1371b339c42bf2","tid":657462,"uid":84840,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote"